const [carrier, setcarrier] = useState({ carrier: "", accountnumber: "", carrieraccountid: "", clave: "", firstname: "", lastname: "", address: "", city: "", state: "", country: "", phone: "", }); const formik = useFormik({ initialValues: { carrier: "ups", accountnumber: "", carrieraccountid: "", clave: "", firstname: "", lastname: "", address: "", city: "", state: "", country: "", phone: "", }, validationSchema, onSubmit: (values) => { /* switch(values.) { case x: // code block break; case y: // code block break; default: // code block }*/ setfedex({ accountnumber: values.accountnumber, }); console.log("PICO PAL QUE LEE", fedex); }, }); return ( <>
